%N A179582 Number of permutations of 1..n+7 with deficiencies #{i: p(i) < i} exceeding the exceedances #{i: p(i) > i} by n or more.
%C A179582 We now have a proof for the given formulas, cf. link. - _M. F. Hasler_, Jul 18 2026
%H A179582 R. J. Mathar, <a href="/A179582/b179582.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..40</a>, terms 1..32 from _R. H. Hardin_
