%F A179582 Empirical: a(n) = 20*a(n-1) -180*a(n-2) +964*a(n-3) -3422*a(n-4) +8484*a(n-5) -15068*a(n-6) +19324*a(n-7) -17769*a(n-8) +11432*a(n-9) -4888*a(n-10) +1248*a(n-11) -144*a(n-12).
%F A179582 Empirical: a(n) = (n+7)*(n+6)*(n^3-23*n^2-148*n+200)/120 +8*(n+7)*(n^2-19*n-222)/3*2^n +729*(n+10)*3^n. - _R. J. Mathar_, Jul 16 2026
%F A179582 a(n) = A179581(n+1) + A179574(n). - _R. J. Mathar_, Jul 18 2026
%F A179582 G.f.: ( 3216 -50489*x +356308*x^2 -1493643*x^3 +4135184*x^4 -7940966*x^5 +10793222*x^6 -10381228*x^7 +6922880*x^8 -3047872*x^9 +797280*x^10 -93888*x^11 ) / ( (-1+3*x)^2*(2*x-1)^4*(x-1)^6 ). - _R. J. Mathar_, Jul 22 2026
%o A179582 (PARI) {A179582(n,N=n+7)=(N+3)*3^(N-1)+N*(N^2-33*N-40)/3<<(N-4)+N*(N-1)*(N^3-44*N^2+321*N-234)/120} \\ _M. F. Hasler_, Jul 18 2026
